== Modifications ==

The original "high-throughput SHA3 core" (Keccak) has been heavily modified by the
current author(s) to:
1. Update the padding and constants to comply with the final FIPS 202
   (SHA3) standard.
2. Implement performance optimizations including [mention specific
   changes like unrolling or pipelining].
3. Re-license the derivative work under the Solderpad Hardware
   License v2.1 to better support physical hardware implementation.

